Titolo: One Piece: Pirate Warriors 3

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: One Piece: Pirate Warriors 3 is an action video game, developed by Omega Force and published by Bandai Namco Entertainment for PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4, PlayStation Vita and Microsoft Windows. The game is the sequel to One Piece: Pirate Warriors 2, released in Japan on March 26, 2015 and subsequently in Western territories on August 25, 2015. This is the last One Piece video game released for the PlayStation 3. An enhanced port for the Nintendo Switch was released in December 2017. It is the third installment in the Pirate Warriors video-game series.
A sequel, One Piece: Pirate Warriors 4, was released in March 2020.

Genere: Action-adventure 

Valutazione: 72
